						 <p>Novote from me, here’s why:</p> <p>This feels like little more than ‘guy who is good at saving lives’, albeit with an anomalous way of doing so. The implications at the end don’t really hit me in any meaningful way, and leave not a huge amount to the imagination. This is in no way a bad article, but it doesn’t do much for me.</p> 
				 	]]>
