					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6109931#post-3831687</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6109931/scp-3542#post-3831687</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 11 Jun 2018 02:27:44 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>MayD</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1422059</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is a Collab with myself and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1528684204" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span>.</p> <p>3542 was inspired by one of us making the joke of &quot;What if Batman was an SCP, and just constantly made the Foundation look incompetent.&quot; The original plan was to write this in less than 48 hours, but then Doomcon happened, so it was put on pause. This is still technically written in under 48 hours, if you look at just how the time we spent on this.</p> 
				 	]]>
